{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Search for a &quot;</strong>Primordial Relic<strong>&quot; that's at the bottom of an abandoned ore mine. The mine is infested with giant ants, who have a leader - a mutant titan who doesn't like visitors. Good luck.</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore the Mine</strong> <strong>in Your Minecart</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046590/extras/AntodonMining.gif?t=1731336738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use a motorized minecart to travel through the mine. Going fast makes a lot of noise and you run the risk of making a wrong turn...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Outsmart or Abuse the Ants</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046590/extras/AntodonAnts.gif?t=1731336738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ants will use various paths within caves to access and mine the gems. Figure out a way to stop them so you can mine the gems yourself.. or use dynamite. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Upgrade the Minecart</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046590/extras/AntodonMerchant.gif?t=1731336738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the gems to fuel the minecart booster or visit the <i>Merchant </i>to buy items and upgrades<br> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Defeat Antodon in the Ultimate Minecart Chase</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046590/extras/AntodonChase.gif?t=1731336738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll need the upgrades because Antodon has his own minecart powered by pure ancient evil and he will not stop until you are derailed.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store